{"id":266668,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/疑似一架殲-7戰機在汕頭市區失事墜毀/","date":"2012-12-04T06:45:19Z","modified":"2017-10-18T22:02:35Z","title":"明镜新闻网 | 一架歼-7战机在汕头市区失事坠毁","content":"<p>本网综合报道，12月4日早上9点多，广东省汕头市护堤路赤窖路段有一架空军飞机失事坠毁，击中一座房屋，导致大火，4人被困，其中1人自行走出，3人受伤已经送往医院救治。驾驶员已跳伞逃生。</p>\n<p>据最新现场图片判读，广东汕头坠毁的飞机为歼击机，而并非有媒体报道的直升机。从垂尾看极有可能是中国空军歼7歼击机。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/%e7%96%91%e4%bc%bc%e4%b8%80%e6%9e%b6%e6%ae%b2-7%e6%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e5%9c%a8%e6%b1%95%e9%a0%ad%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%80%e5%a4%b1%e4%ba%8b%e5%a2%9c%e6%af%80/u2143p1247t1d30313f73dt20121204120616/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-266670\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-266670\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120616.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120616.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120616-300x209.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友质疑</p>\n<p>官方消息称，机上驾驶员在坠毁瞬间已跳伞逃生。消息一出，有网友质疑，直升机驾驶员怎么能跳伞？一般直升机都是靠减震设备减轻坠落瞬间造成的人员伤害。目前世界上仅俄罗斯的卡-50，卡-52武装直升机能弹射跳伞，先炸掉旋翼和座舱盖，然后弹射。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/%e7%96%91%e4%bc%bc%e4%b8%80%e6%9e%b6%e6%ae%b2-7%e6%88%b0%e6%a9%9f%e5%9c%a8%e6%b1%95%e9%a0%ad%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%80%e5%a4%b1%e4%ba%8b%e5%a2%9c%e6%af%80/u2143p1247t1d30313f73dt20121204120617/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-266671\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-266671\" title=\"U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120617\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120617.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"337\" height=\"548\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120617.jpg 337w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/U2143P1247T1D30313F73DT20121204120617-184x300.jpg 184w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>最新：据央视新闻官方微博发布消息称，经广东消防确认，今日上午9时左右在汕头坠毁的飞机为歼-7战斗机。</p>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18269,19168,8779],"tags":[18629,33422,19193,13850,18941,14981]}